text: {'text': 'Regular pet shop that sells both parrots and fish. Reasonably priced pet food. Not a lot of selection for aquatic fish but I’m sure it serves the area well. Owners are always willing to share their knowledge and experience on how best to care for them.', 'languageCode': 'en'}
